snippet.title: Millennials – We are changing to CAMPUS LIFE! 🎓
snippet.description:
The big day is here! Join us along with the journey from Millennials to Campus Life! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2103090
If you’re as excited as we are about the game, get ready for Steam Next Fest in June where you’ll be able to play the game!

Join our official Frozen Way Discord to become a member of our amazing community!
- Have access to exclusive content from our games!
- Discuss with other players!
- Get in touch with the devs!
https://discord.gg/frozenwayofficial

Join our Social media channels to keep up to date:
Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/frozenWay 
Twitter:  https://twitter.com/FrozenWayGames
